QMS Lite publishes reusable quality-system content and automation in a split-license model:

- code and automation artifacts: Apache-2.0
- SOPs, WIs, templates, docs, and example seed content: CC BY 4.0

This repository also contains fictional company/example material used to dogfood the workflow model. Adopters are expected to validate suitability, tailor company-owned files, and operate their own controlled repositories.
